title: Tomas Berdych Wins His 1st ATP Tour Title of Season
text:
Published By: NYTimes Tennis - Today 
Top-seeded Tomas Berdych won his 11th ATP Tour title by defeating Guillermo Garcia-Lopez 6-3, 7-6 (7) Monday in the Shenzhen Open final....
